728587f-a.title: Richmond: Bell Street - Fletcher Street
728587f-a.text:
52 Bell Street, south side, between Fletcher and Oak Streets
(Rosebank), showing the rear of the house. Bell Street was formerly
Wall Street.
July 12, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
